  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 09/26/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.11-MinorChanges\">Minor Changes</h3><ul><li><p>The Rev/Rallio integration now looks for either a phone number or an email address where, prior, both were required.</p></li><li><p>Improved the Payment Request Modal UI for readability and usability.</p></li><li><p>Square is now disabled when the Square account is disconnected from RepairQ.</p></li><li><p>Added a setting to toggle <strong>Tip Amount</strong> (found under <em><strong>Settings \u2192 Templates \u2192 Receipts</strong></em>) option which allows customers to see the amount they tipped on their receipt and / or invoice.</p></li><li><p>Added the ability to see Change Log history for catalog item compatibility\u00a0.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.11-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Resolved an issue that stops Square devices from functioning after a device code reset.</p></li><li><p>Refurbishment tickets now retain their items' original costs.</p></li><li><p>Instock issue, which could sometimes visually be absent in the Inventory Summary, now displays correctly again.</p></li></ul>",
      "representation": "export_view",
